      <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed">{post.description}</p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <section class="mb-12">
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">HVAC contractors, mechanical equipment suppliers, and industrial distributors across Malaysia ship air conditioning units, compressors, pumps, and control systems that require specialized protective packaging. Honeycomb cardboard provides the combination of lightweight efficiency and heavy-duty impact protection essential for mechanical equipment reaching installation sites safely.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Honeycomb Protection for Industrial Equipment</h2>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Superior Shock Absorption for Vibration-Sensitive Components</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">HVAC compressors and refrigeration systems are sensitive to vibration and impact damage during transport. Honeycomb's cellular structure absorbs shock energy, protecting internal components during highway transport across Selangor and Peninsular Malaysia.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Lightweight Design Reduces Shipping Costs</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Unlike wood crating or foam packaging, honeycomb is significantly lighter. Equipment suppliers reduce dimensional weight shipping charges while maintaining superior protection standards for HVAC units and industrial machinery.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Moisture & Humidity Protection in Tropical Climate</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Malaysia's humidity threatens electrical components and metal surfaces. Combine honeycomb with moisture barriers and desiccant packets. This dual protection prevents rust, corrosion, and moisture ingress during storage and long-distance transport.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Custom Sizing for Equipment Dimensions</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Each HVAC unit and industrial equipment has unique dimensions. Honeycomb can be custom-cut to fit compressors, air handlers, condensing units, and control panels precisely, eliminating gaps and ensuring maximum protection.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Packaging HVAC Systems for Safe Delivery</h2>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Multi-Layer Construction for Large AC Units</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Layer thick honeycomb (50mm) around all sides of AC outdoor units and indoor units. Secure with corrugated outer shells and industrial strapping. This multi-layer approach protects against crushing and vibration during truck transport from Balakong warehouse to installation sites.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Bracing & Securing Heavy Components</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Use internal honeycomb bracing to prevent equipment shifting during transport. Create compartments for compressors, piping, and electrical controls. Secure with polypropylene straps to prevent movement on highways across KL, Cheras, and Kajang.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Foam & Honeycomb Hybrid Approach</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Combine foam corner protectors with honeycomb padding for maximum protection. This hybrid approach adds minimal weight while protecting delicate fins, tubes, and electrical connections on HVAC equipment.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Quality Assurance & Testing</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Professional equipment suppliers should conduct drop tests or vibration simulations to verify packaging adequacy. Honeycomb from Quinocycle meets industrial standards and can withstand rigorous testing protocols for HVAC and machinery shipments.</p>
      </section>

